{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDkxMDAxNDI1", "number": 1580, "title": "Include common (engine-level) args in help output by default.", "bodyText": "Picard tools do not display common arguments (TMP_DIR, VALIDATION_STRINGENCY, or COMPRESSION_LEVEL, to name a few) in command line help output unless the user explicitly requests them using capital -H, or --stdhelp. This isn't obvious to users and it makes it hard to find these arguments (see broadinstitute/gatk#6811).\nThis PR changes this behavior so that common args are displayed by default when the user asks for help or when a command line parsing error is detected. If approved, we'll need to make a corresponding change to the usage calls made by the parsers themselves so the behavior is the same when the user asks for help via -h.", "createdAt": "2020-09-22T14:56:51Z", "url": "https://github.com/broadinstitute/picard/pull/1580", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "c473474b8c9850db7054256961673ef425ad0941"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2021-02-08T21:36:37Z", "author": {"login": "cmnbroad"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 4, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdLKoctAH2gAyNDkxMDAxNDI1OjE0OTljMWIzOWE4YzdkMTEwZTZjZWIxOWYzNWYzNjFkODQzNjcxMTQ=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABd4OSwSgFqTU4NTk0NTE4Mw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "1499c1b39a8c7d110e6ceb19f35f361d84367114", "author": {"user": {"login": "cmnbroad", "name": "Chris Norman"}}, "url": "https://github.com/broadinstitute/picard/commit/1499c1b39a8c7d110e6ceb19f35f361d84367114", "committedDate": "2020-09-21T21:53:38Z", "message": "Include common (engine-level) args in help output."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTYxMjk1NTAz", "url": "https://github.com/broadinstitute/picard/pull/1580#pullrequestreview-561295503", "createdAt": "2021-01-04T19:46:43Z", "commit": {"oid": "1499c1b39a8